messages.content: Hey there, I'm Militidas, just a hunter from a nearby village. Nice to meet you. What brings you here to Agia Marina?
messages.speaker: Militidas Stanis

messages.content: Insurgents? I haven't seen any around here. As a hunter, I spend a lot of time in the surrounding areas, and I would have noticed any suspicious activity. Are you guys part of some sort of operation or mission?
messages.speaker: Militidas Stanis
